<ul class="list1">

<li>
<b>2026-2027 School Year - Nursery and Kindergarten Admissions Application  <!--<img src="../images/new.gif">-->
 </b><br><br>
 
<span class="text-danger">Date of ‘Online Enrollment Application’:<br>
<b><u>2/7/2025 – 31/10/2025</u></b></span><br><br>

<span class="text-success">Date of ‘Submission or Postal Enrollment Application’:<br>
<b><u>7/7/2025 – 31/10/2025</u></b></span>
<br>
</li>
	
<li>
<b>2025-2026 School Year - Nursery and Kindergarten Admissions Application 
 </b><br><br>
 
For the 2025-2026 school year, the AM and PM classes of <u>Pre-Nursery</u> (2 years old), and the PM classes of <u>Nursery Class</u> (3 years old), <u>Lower Kindergarten</u> (4 years old) and <u>Upper Kindergarten</u> (5 years old) have a few remaining spaces.  Enrollment applications are currently being accepted. Interested parents should download the 'Enrollment Application Form', mail or submit it in person to the School Office with the required documents. <br><br>
For further information or to apply, please enquire on 2491 1082 or click here <img src="../images/finger.jpg"> <a href="admissions_process.asp">Admissions</a>
</li>
